# On-chain activity monitor — local config
# Copy to ".env.onchain-activity" (gitignored, and the filename is namespaced so
# it will NOT clash with any other .env on the machine), then set your RPC URL.
#
# The ONLY sensitive value in this project: your Solana RPC URL. Provider URLs
# (HelloMoon, Helius, Triton, ...) embed an access token in the path, so treat
# the whole URL as a secret. If unset, the app falls back to the public
# endpoint, which is rate-limited and flaky under this tool's load.
#
# Format example:  SOLANA_RPC=https://<your-node>.fleet.hellomoon.io/<token>

SOLANA_RPC=
